---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Home">

  <!-- ===== Hero ===== -->
<section class="mb-16">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 sm:flex-row sm:items-center">
    <img
      src="/images/profile/me.webp"
      alt="Katsuhiro Yamakawa"
      class="h-20 w-20 shrink-0 rounded-full object-cover sm:h-24 sm:w-24"
    />
    <div>
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 sm:text-3xl dark:text-poi-focus">
        Katsuhiro Yamakawa
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-2 font-sans text-base leading-7 text-zinc-600 dark:text-poi-muted">
        Builder / Operator
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

  <!-- ===== Theme ===== -->
  <section class="mb-16 max-w-3xl">
  <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-light-accent pl-5 dark:border-poi-accent">
    <p class="font-sans text-lg italic leading-8 text-zinc-600 dark:text-poi-muted">
      Systems that disappear into the workflow.
    </p>
  </blockquote>
  <p class="mt-5 font-sans text-base leading-8 text-zinc-700 dark:text-poi-focus/90">
    現場のカオスをちょうどいい粒感のシステムに。
  </p>
</section>

  <!-- ===== Works ===== -->
  <section class="mb-16 max-w-3xl">
    <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-poi-focus">Works</h2>
      <a class="cactus-link text-sm" href="/works/">すべて見る →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-5 dark:border-poi-border dark:bg-poi-panel">
        <p class="font-mono text-xs" style="color:#5de4c7;">現場 · 業務自動化</p>
        <h3 class="mt-1 font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-poi-focus">NFC Attendance System</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 font-sans text-sm leading-7 text-zinc-600 dark:text-poi-muted">
          Sony RC-S300 と Raspberry Pi 2 で作った勤怠管理。カードをかざすだけで記録が完結。給与自動計算システム。
        </p>
        <div class="mt-3 flex gap-4 font-mono text-xs">
          <a class="hover:underline" style="color:#5de4c7;" href="/nfc-attendance/">Demo →</a>
          <a class="hover:underline" style="color:#5de4c7;" href="/posts/nfc-attendance-system/">制作記事</a>
          <a class="hover:underline" style="color:#5de4c7;" href="https://github.com/yktsnet/nfc-attendance-kit" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-5 dark:border-poi-border dark:bg-poi-panel">
        <p class="font-mono text-xs" style="color:#addb67;">IoT · プロダクト</p>
        <h3 class="mt-1 font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-poi-focus">Cat Feed Tracker</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 font-sans text-sm leading-7 text-zinc-600 dark:text-poi-muted">
          Pico W のリードスイッチで給餌棚の開閉を検知し、FastAPI + PostgreSQL で記録。LINE で家族に定時通知・照会・設定変更ができる家庭向け IoT システム。
        </p>
        <div class="mt-3 flex gap-4 font-mono text-xs">
          <a class="hover:underline" style="color:#addb67;" href="/cat-feed-tracker/">Demo →</a>
          <a class="hover:underline" style="color:#addb67;" href="/posts/cat-feed-tracker/">制作記事</a>
          <a class="hover:underline" style="color:#addb67;" href="https://github.com/yktsnet/cat-feed-tracker" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-5 dark:border-poi-border dark:bg-poi-panel">
        <p class="font-mono text-xs" style="color:#89ddff;">運用基盤 · 可視化</p>
        <h3 class="mt-1 font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-poi-focus">Live Demo (Trading System)</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 font-sans text-sm leading-7 text-zinc-600 dark:text-poi-muted">
          自動売買パイプラインのログを Cloudflare KV 経由で集約し、Astro SSR でリアルタイムに表示するダッシュボード。
        </p>
        <div class="mt-3 flex gap-4 font-mono text-xs">
          <a class="hover:underline" style="color:#89ddff;" href="/live-demo/">Live Demo →</a>
          <a class="hover:underline" style="color:#89ddff;" href="/posts/live-demo/">制作記事</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Explore ===== -->
  <section class="mb-14 max-w-3xl">
    <div class="space-y-3">
      <p class="font-sans text-base leading-8 text-zinc-700 dark:text-poi-focus/90">
        <a class="cactus-link" href="/posts/">Posts</a>
        <span class="text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400"> — </span>
        設計の背景や判断の理由を書いています。
      </p>
      <p class="font-sans text-base leading-8 text-zinc-700 dark:text-poi-focus/90">
        <a class="cactus-link" href="/contact/">Contact</a>
        <span class="text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400"> — </span>
        お問い合わせ・各種リンク。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</MainLayout>
